data.description: Large 5 bedroom home(no additions, actually 5 bedrooms) plus 2 car garage (no conversion) is ready to move into. Easy access to schools, shopping, transportation, Roberto Cruz Leadership Academy charter highschool, Alum Rock Park, Hwy 680 and more. Start the new year with room to spread out! Enjoy entertaining family and friends this freshly painted home. Familyroom would be ideal large eating area with room for everyone. Central air conditioning, double cedar lined closets in most bedrooms ,new LVN flooring in kitchen and family room.  Convenient corner location provides extra parking. Great floorplan with room to spread out.
